title: Donald Trump Warned Us About Himself: A Closer Look | Michael Barbaro | Alex Baze & Dan McElroy
description:
Seth takes a closer look at Donald Trump kicking off his first foreign trip as president under a cloud of suspicion. (0:20)
Then, Seth and Michael Barbaro discuss how the unpredictability of the Trump administration affects New York Times' podcast, The Daily. (8:30)
In a new Late Night Chats segment, head writer Alex Baze talks to field coordinator Dan McElroy. (18:37)
